        <updateDate>2008-08-23T15:47:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Noose Hate Crime Act of 2008 - Amends the federal criminal code to impose a fine and/or prison term of up to two years on anyone who, with intent to harass or intimidate any person because of that person's race, religion, or national origin, displays a noose in public. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
